snippet.title: We Wished Nawaz Sharif, Got Uri In Return: Sushma Swaraj

localized.description:
Speaking at the UN, Foreign Minister Sushma Swaraj hurled criticism at Pakistani PM Nawaz Sharif for his comments in the General Assembly, and said that despite two years of an unprecedented outreach, India has been meted a series of deadly terror attacks by Pakistan, most recently at the army camp in Uri near the border in Kashmir, where 18 soldiers were killed just days ago.

Watch full speech: http://www.ndtv.com/video/news/news/watch-sushma-swaraj-s-takedown-of-pak-at-un-432701?yt
